summary: An ordinance accepting the awards in the condemnations for elevated highway structures, approaches and bridges in the vicinities of 1st Avenue South and Michigan Street and 1st Avenue South and West Myrtle Street and for the widening of Highland Park Way, in connection therewith, under Ordinances Nos. 82137, 82138 and 82492, King County Superior Court Cause Nos. 460721, 460720 and 465381, respectively; and providing for payment out of moneys appropriated by Ordinance No. 81862 as amended.
